precis:
Amendments (SCHEDULE NO. 819) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which will
allow for the addition of certain additives and fillers to "surimi", a
blend of prepared fish that has the appearance and taste of a marine or of
a freshwater animal.
